{"tid":244804,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"龍鎮洋：逢中必反是香港避免共產黨化的唯一出路","createTime":"2017-05-15T17:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T12:51:43.000Z","uid":17232,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52bbe63ee60e69904fa7eec0511e9829d2114dc6","tid":244804,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"龍鎮洋《香港文革將潮入高潮》：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港是中國尚未完成共產黨化和文革化的地方，很多香港人也未曾見識過共產黨統治的恐怖、邪惡及殘暴。<br />\n<br />\n七警案引發的警界反彈，表明香港警界的政治幼稚和目光短淺。如果他們以為中共的大陸是他們的依靠和同盟，他們就大錯特錯了，他們最後的結局會比曾蔭權更慘烈！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人請記住一句話－－逢中必反是香港可以避免共產黨化和文革化禍亂的唯一出路！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/010143_f9fb40b3cf31655cad0e1417ecdd4173.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F010143_f9fb40b3cf31655cad0e1417ecdd4173.jpg&h=d3ec53e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b7338ca568476f7c9e7e8c35bee007fe661b670","tid":244804,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232d36abf409d8119e5c87f3f1167b478b024597","tid":244804,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307ccb3a74553bcc392bf84d45fe95914d4a51ea","tid":244804,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e11470909bba6596e6a2ca433444ba24c32acfb","tid":244804,"uid":17232,"like":0,"